{"tid":297901,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【身有屎】24歲支那大學生，電話騙案被騙440萬人民幣。","createTime":"2017-06-26T00:00:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-26T15:31:56.000Z","uid":37661,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"593ad1329a2fc1a53f991dc1951829fe6a83d45a","tid":297901,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T00:00:01.000Z","msg":"女子疑遇電話騙案被騙去440萬元人民幣<br />\n<br />\n25/6/2017 23:52<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;再有市民懷疑遇到電話騙案, 被騙去440萬元人民幣.<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;一名24歲女子下午到將軍澳警署報案, 指早前接獲一名不明男子來電, 指事主涉嫌與一宗刑事案件有關, 電話其後轉駁至一名自稱內地執法人員的男子, 事主按他的指示, 先後十一次將合共四百四十萬元人民幣, 存到一個內地銀行戶口, 之後懷疑受騙報警. 警方將案件列作以欺騙手段取得財產, 暫時未有人被捕.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?NewsId=20170625235206\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metroradio.com.hk%2Fnews%2Flive.aspx%3FNewsId%3D20170625235206&d=cqr16t5r9tUJDj39CKmzKgRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=8bf4b187\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?NewsId=20170625235206</a>"},{"pid":"52ca2df2fb39f9600d21cadac9ac56b914ff7a5f","tid":297901,"uid":19406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T00:00:33.000Z","msg":"咁有錢？"},{"pid":"2329bb2d9efb353089ae95a0d7944648ad223466","tid":297901,"uid":44105,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T00:01:43.000Z","msg":"洗白白<br />\n咁就洗白左4百萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89be2f51d33248147befc6e47fc7fb91f381dcc0","tid":297901,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T00:02:38.000Z","msg":"將軍澳有一名內地女學生懷疑被電話行騙，損失約四百四十萬元人民幣。 <br />\n<br />\n警方指受害女事主24歲，昨日傍晚到將軍澳警署報警，表示收到一名男子電話，指她涉及一宗刑事案件，電話隨即轉到另一名，自稱是內地執法人員的男子，指示她分十一次將四百四十萬元人民幣存到一個內地戶口。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/local/5950093c6db28c491c035128\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Flocal%2F5950093c6db28c491c035128&d=cqr16t5r9tUJDj39CKmzKgRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=57c67736\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/local/5950093c6db28c491c035128</a>"},{"pid":"f90290d83804acceb004018fc965cd48f4773ada","tid":297901,"uid":74289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T00:02:44.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d7c959dd7388ef93ab3fef91d5d6a6752ecf9cc","tid":297901,"uid":25560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T00:04:22.000Z","msg":"新聞講左咁多次都中招<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e6efae16375e3124ba87898fdc3cce8f5fa5a97","tid":297901,"uid":6604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T00:05:32.000Z","msg":"呢班支那大學生來香港讀書<br />\n唔睇 local news<br />\n<br />\n可能每晚都係喺屋企都係睇支央電視台 / 湖南衞視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3440972c180aa37ee6b1cde0e4cd4110f0f5612c","tid":297901,"uid":37661,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T00:07:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢班支那大學生來香港讀書<br />\n唔睇 local news<br />\n<br />\n可能每晚都係喺屋企都係睇支央電視台 / 湖南衞視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係唔撚抵可憐"},{"pid":"a24fa2d47414022e825e26f9edb4735d1b2a6be7","tid":297901,"uid":32390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T00:09:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢班支那大學生來香港讀書<br />\n唔睇 local news<br />\n<br />\n可能每晚都係喺屋企都係睇支央電視台 / 湖南衞視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係唔撚抵可憐</blockquote><br />\npetty cash only"},{"pid":"13b4000c308b75539f16f3d626ac2ce3bb9e050c","tid":297901,"uid":35296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T00:09:43.000Z","msg":"人地轉緊錢走你地就以為佢比人呃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/